To install simple move the .pl perl script to ~/.config/hexchat/addons or ~/.config/xchat/addons

Start HexChat/Xchat and navigate to Window>Plugins and scripts>Load>navigate to location of .pl script and load it.

You will need the hexchat-perl plugin installed:                 

sudo apt install hexchat-perl

Type /bhelp in hexchat/xchat for list of commands

